text: Reda Ribinskaitė (born 8 June 1966) is a Lithuanian rower. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Lithuanian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Soviet Union Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Marijampolė
